latestIgtvVideos.title: Am I even approachable?
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
They roast you, they insult you, they body shame you and then they expect you to seek help from them 😊 
It’s very easy to pass on our responsibilities as a society, we need to reflect upon ourselves. 
Are we even approachable to help someone out there struggling? No body likes to talk about their problems to someone who’d belittle them or judge them that’s why most of us feel suffocated and just give up on life. 
It’s easy to judge and difficult to reflect. #ripsushantsinghrajput💔

latestIgtvVideos.title: Soft pink summer eye makeup.
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
The longer I stay at home the more homeless I’m gonna look 😝 it’s been a while since I filmed something for my IGTV. This lockdown has helped me to slow down and reflect on myself.

Thought of creating this look and felt really therapeutic to have done something for my creative health. Filming videos, editing them, writing scripts, selecting songs the whole process has always given me lots of hope and good vibes. It helps to change my thoughts, feelings and ability to manage life events. 
I hope you all take out time for yourself and work on that secret project of yours. Its alright if it sucks, all of us here are trying :) Products used :

latestIgtvVideos.title: Natural dewy everyday makeup.
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
While I might not be able to change my skin, I can change my mindset. - Unknown.

Well, apparently I’m tired wishing for a pore less, perfect flawless skin portrayed in those air brushes ads and facetuned Instagrams. Tried all sorts of routines, went on a vegan diet, got a grip on my stress level but still they tend to come up every now and then and it’s here to stay. 
So here I’m embracing and accepting my blemishes. You might as well make peace with your flaws cause sometimes we need to show some kindness to ourselves which we freely give to others.  Let’s reject those unrealistic beauty standards. You really don’t need a concealer to hide those scars. You know what? Screw it, cause I woke up like this 🤗 Skin positivity is the need of the hour. 
Also I love how my makeup skills are getting better 😋 this one is indeed a very easy simple tutorial. 
Products used

Kajal : Miss Claire brown kohl : Sima brown. 
Eyeliner : @blueheavencosmetics 
Blush : Wet N wild colour icon : Mellow wine. 
Lipstick : Wet N wild : Give me mocha + Lakmé enrich matte : Bm11 
Highlighter : Makeup revolution brick highlighter.

latestIgtvVideos.title: Ooty- Travelogue 🌸😍
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Better to see something once than to hear about it a thousand times. 
I decide to make a travelogue out of these tiny bits and pieces of my recent ooty trip.  I recorded everything on my phone and it was indeed very impromptu of me to make this travelogue. 
Past 3 days had been so good, I was so close to the nature. 🥺🌲 Friends that turned into family, places that turned into memories. ❤️
